    public interface EndPathMultiplicity
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'End Path Multiplicity'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Property
    • Lower
    • Upper

      • getLower

        int getLower()
        Returns the value of the 'Lower' attribute. The default value is "0". Gives the minimum number of values of the property at the end of the related bindingPath, for each object reached by navigation along the bindingPath from an instance of the block owning the property to which EndPathMultiplicity is applied
        Returns:
